    "description": "BeMap, Inc. engages in the mobile system integration business in Japan. The company operates through Mobility Innovation, Wireless Innovation, and Solution Business segments. It offers systems for railways, including route search services, as well as allows railway service companies to provide users with information using content management system (CMS) Wi-Fi infrastructures. The company also develops and maintains CMS for Wi-Fi; and Wi-Fi authentication systems that supports public wireless LAN services for telecommunication carriers. In addition, it provides systems for individuals to use a public wireless LAN at railway stations, airports, convenience stores, restaurants, and other places through telecommunication carriers and railway operators; and cloud-based digital video recording services. Further, the company offers 02020, an on-air to online to offline solution; TV metadata services; MMS business, content print business; and website/software development services. BeMap, Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
